tory.go` | `SharedInformerFactory` |\n| `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Group informer accessor |\n| `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | v1alpha1 informer accessors |\n| `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Lister expansion interfaces |\n\n**API Group:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`  \n**CRD Types:** `AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`  \n**Regeneration:** `make gen-client` via `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n\n---\n\n### 3. pkg/agentd Code (AR-018: Idle Cleanup Controller)\n\n**Location:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/agentd/`\n\n**Files (3):**\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `pkg/agentd/const.go` | `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute` |\n| `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | `Reconciler` struct with `Reconcile()` and `SetupWithManager()` methods |\n| `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` | 10 unit tests covering all reconcile paths |\n\n**Binary Entry Point:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/agentd/main.go`\n\n**Supporting file:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` defines `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n\n---\n\n### 4. AR-018 Spec Documents (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\n\n**Location:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/`\n\n| File | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `changes/AR-018/proposal.md` | Purpose, scope, architecture, impact analysis, acceptance criteria |\n| `changes/AR-018/design.md` | Full technical design (569 lines): architecture, data flow, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy, deployment manifests, implementation steps |\n| `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md` | 14 requirements with 35+ GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios (352 lines) |\n| `chan