ypes.go` | Shared types (TargetPort, SandboxTemplate, etc.) |\n| `constants.go` | Constants |\n| `groupversion_info.go` | GroupVersion registration |\n| `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Generated deep copy functions |\n\n**Sandbox CRD (external):** Imported from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` -- defined at `pkg/apis/agents/v1alpha1/sandbox_types.go`\n\n---\n\n### 7. Full pkg/ Directory Structure\n\n```\npkg/\n  agentd/\n    const.go\n    reconciler.go\n    reconciler_test.go\n  apis/\n    agents/v1alpha1/\n      sandbox_types.go\n      zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n    runtime/v1alpha1/\n      agent_type.go, agent_type_test.go\n      codeinterpreter_types.go, codeinterpreter_types_test.go\n      constants.go, constants_test.go\n      doc.go\n      groupversion_info.go, groupversion_info_test.go\n      shared_types.go, shared_types_test.go\n      zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n  common/types/\n    types.go\n  picod/\n    (server, auth, config, execute, health, files/*)\n  router/\n    (server, proxy, jwt, middleware, loadbalancer, backend, session_manager, informer, health, config, errors)\n  store/\n    (store.go, codec.go, singleton.go, store_redis.go, store_valkey.go)\n  workloadmanager/\n    const.go\n    handler/ (sandbox_lifecycle.go, sandbox_create.go, sandbox_delete.go, models.go, constants.go)\n    reconciler/ (reconciler.go, types.go, sync.go, pod.go, agentruntime.go, codeinterpreter.go, event_handlers.go, metrics.go)\n    response/ (response.go)\n```\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287402d15ffe5gAR1J8Lp0TtkB","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775847330534,"end":1775847471713}}}}
